{"tid":166992,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"數學低能懇心受教］小學雞數學問題","createTime":"2017-03-22T14:09:53.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-22T16:46:47.000Z","uid":25232,"like":0,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"55401bdc3cb3d7d1f67f9986e4c5f15424ea939a","tid":166992,"uid":25232,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-22T14:09:53.000Z","msg":"記得小學個陣上數學堂教正負數個陣<br />\n正負得負<br />\n正正得正<br />\n負負得正<br />\n<br />\n個陣我問miss 點解負負得正？<br />\n佢話係公式 記就得 <br />\n<br />\n有無巴打可以解釋下點解負負會係正？<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 白痴問題唔好屌"},{"pid":"5e07bef717908d7aa6c11627a08c3a9ebe863846","tid":166992,"uid":85819,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-22T14:14:03.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"2d1df4a5efc365411d75e930d1a1be556e2bd71d","tid":166992,"uid":8212,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-22T14:14:37.000Z","msg":"簡單啲講<br />\n可以話係因為-1 x -1<br />\n本身已經carry一個負 再有一個負<br />\n將佢再負多次 變返一個正"},{"pid":"4c55534ef33419339bf52f37031cc6f264dca3d5","tid":166992,"uid":8212,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-22T14:15:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>留名<br />\n<br />\n我差人2蚊 再差人2蚊 再差人2蚊<br />\n<br />\n唔係差人6蚊咩點解變左正數?</blockquote><br />\n你個個係-2 + -2 + -2<br />\n並唔係 -2-2-2"},{"pid":"02555f98ecf6f1a27781cf56ead8fee691d7f2ee","tid":166992,"uid":8212,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-22T14:16:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>留名<br />\n<br />\n我差人2蚊 再差人2蚊 再差人2蚊<br />\n<br />\n唔係差人6蚊咩點解變左正數?</blockquote><br />\n你個個係-2 + -2 + -2<br />\n並唔係 -2-2-2</blockquote><br />\n自膠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n講得唔清楚<br />\n因為你爭人錢<br />\n對你嚟講係負 人哋先係正"},{"pid":"3b435fcfe5ab69e1beecee957d1dfaf81e533ed8","tid":166992,"uid":25232,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-22T14:16:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>簡單啲講<br />\n可以話係因為-1 x -1<br />\n本身已經carry一個負 再有一個負<br />\n將佢再負多次 變返一個正</blockquote><br />\n都係唔明<br />\n點解我唔可以再carry 多個負？ <br />\n好亂呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a414addf606ec212dde4f7144170a68b867c77e0","tid":166992,"uid":25232,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-22T14:18:00.000Z","msg":"洗唔洗咁快有負皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"39e485e62a70b884f2f3663f973ae1b96bd079af","tid":166992,"uid":74019,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-22T14:19:18.000Z","msg":"0<br />\n=(0)(-1)<br />\n=(1-1)(-1)<br />\n=(1)(-1)+(-1)(-1)<br />\n=-1+(-1)(-1) <br />\n=&gt; (-1)(-1)=1"},{"pid":"d83afe528a2d4b6ebac9ebc29e16bf43cd3ccef1","tid":166992,"uid":28800,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-22T14:19:47.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"952b1a520629516005651a1e0cc85756153d5c9c","tid":166992,"uid":8212,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-22T14:21:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>簡單啲講<br />\n可以話係因為-1 x -1<br />\n本身已經carry一個負 再有一個負<br />\n將佢再負多次 變返一個正</blockquote><br />\n都係唔明<br />\n點解我唔可以再carry 多個負？ <br />\n好亂呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n一個負嘅負係係咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 而家係講緊乘唔係加減"},{"pid":"e7c63689802e2c5a593c9f5b86f875534275ebee","tid":166992,"uid":43880,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-22T14:23:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>洗唔洗咁快有負皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n等我俾多個負皮睇下會唔會變正先<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/35.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3c2fbcaa8a523ea22cd59453489e6d3d6388b0e6","tid":166992,"uid":74019,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-22T14:26:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>簡單啲講<br />\n可以話係因為-1 x -1<br />\n本身已經carry一個負 再有一個負<br />\n將佢再負多次 變返一個正</blockquote><br />\n都係唔明<br />\n點解我唔可以再carry 多個負？ <br />\n好亂呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n一個負嘅負係係咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 而家係講緊乘唔係加減</blockquote><br />\na+(-a)=0 for all number a<br />\nlet b=-a<br />\nb+(-b)=0<br />\n=&gt; -a+(--a)=0<br />\n=&gt; --a=a"},{"pid":"82227cacb4c1871e925e66bbc94dcc5f972ae96d","tid":166992,"uid":25232,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-22T14:26:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>0<br />\n=(0)(-1)<br />\n=(1-1)(-1)<br />\n=(1)(-1)+(-1)(-1)<br />\n=-1+(-1)(-1) <br />\n=&gt; (-1)(-1)=1</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n明啦"},{"pid":"0f219f055295f73e4ca32b1dd73f323413a59cb1","tid":166992,"uid":25232,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-22T14:27:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>簡單啲講<br />\n可以話係因為-1 x -1<br />\n本身已經carry一個負 再有一個負<br />\n將佢再負多次 變返一個正</blockquote><br />\n都係唔明<br />\n點解我唔可以再carry 多個負？ <br />\n好亂呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n一個負嘅負係係咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 而家係講緊乘唔係加減</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n屌還屌 細力少少<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d2315e4a36829cec6f56b3a2793d90b1215524de","tid":166992,"uid":31254,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-22T14:28:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>0<br />\n=(0)(-1)<br />\n=(1-1)(-1)<br />\n=(1)(-1)+(-1)(-1)<br />\n=-1+(-1)(-1) <br />\n=&gt; (-1)(-1)=1</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n明啦</blockquote><br />\n小學畢業未"},{"pid":"b1ebaf8e398a7684e7a49fd604c8e9940e508763","tid":166992,"uid":70527,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-22T14:29:03.000Z","msg":"當語言既雙重否定"},{"pid":"d08a9b3c301fb0fe0ff31335693c4f3968bdbd16","tid":166992,"uid":34771,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-22T14:29:20.000Z","msg":"我差2個人$5  2*(-5)=-10<br />\n2個人差我$5 (-2)*(-5)=10"},{"pid":"02b86f1a4d04b9b6c5a0fb4d405cc01bef81e074","tid":166992,"uid":14653,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-22T14:29:52.000Z","msg":"反面嘅反面=正面"},{"pid":"29aac0ec2b00046e3d014c0bb35cf55e04345c8a","tid":166992,"uid":25232,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-22T14:38:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>0<br />\n=(0)(-1)<br />\n=(1-1)(-1)<br />\n=(1)(-1)+(-1)(-1)<br />\n=-1+(-1)(-1) <br />\n=&gt; (-1)(-1)=1</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n明啦</blockquote><br />\n小學畢業未</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n比你地話下無咩所謂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n最重要係知道點解 <br />\n多謝咁多位巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b9ffe6f446a61308ea5d3a6971a5edda02634834","tid":166992,"uid":1845,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-22T14:42:12.000Z","msg":"用距離 除 速率 等於時間 代入正負數時所代表的意義 你就知道負負係會得正"},{"pid":"da88c3b7f78a4129c19732890d4703282b2683d4","tid":166992,"uid":5247,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-22T14:45:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>留名<br />\n<br />\n我差人2蚊 再差人2蚊 再差人2蚊<br />\n<br />\n唔係差人6蚊咩點解變左正數?</blockquote><br />\n-2+(-2)+(-2)<br />\n=-2-2-2<br />\n=-6<br />\n負負得正係乘數先就咁直接睇<br />\n加減數要係用於拆括號<br />\n<br />\nSorry for1999...<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0498ec07b0f58f2854efc8c466b63fd0fb07aac3","tid":166992,"uid":41742,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-22T14:47:50.000Z","msg":"-1係代表1嘅addictive inverse<br />\n-(-1)即係-1嘅addictive inverse，即係1"},{"pid":"68e9b80b53a5ef4f6ef10bc1d39032b381f79ed3","tid":166992,"uid":89683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-22T14:50:05.000Z","msg":"算式上唔難，但意義上呢手？<br />\n<br />\n負負得正可以係好深<br />\n<br />\na x  3= a+a+a<br />\n咁a x (-3)代表乜"},{"pid":"7356dce3a502e788e1f16e46ab4c21c9acad3b2f","tid":166992,"uid":838,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-22T14:55:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>算式上唔難，但意義上呢手？<br />\n<br />\n負負得正可以係好深<br />\n<br />\na x  3= a+a+a<br />\n咁a x (-3)代表乜</blockquote><br />\n點解要搵嘢嚟代表呢件事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n乘就係乘，係一種數學法則，無其他嘢可以演譯到同一意思<br />\n<br />\n用加數嚟做示範只可以演譯狹義乘數，唔係乘嘅全部"},{"pid":"d15b335cd6a0881c8f4ecab784ca97789abdb7d3","tid":166992,"uid":838,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-22T14:56:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>-1係代表1嘅addictive inverse<br />\n-(-1)即係-1嘅addictive inverse，即係1</blockquote><br />\nSimple and nice solution<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}